snippet.title: Halo CE+ X (Original Xbox) Release Trailer
snippet.description:
GO BEYOND.
DOWNLOAD:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/halo-ce/downloads/halo-ce-x-original-xbox

The complete Xbox release of Halo CE+ is here! featuring 13 multiplayer maps, a new menu, bonus features and more.  This mod is for the original Xbox release of Halo Combat Evolved (NTSC) and is not compatible with MCC.

Halo CE+ X features the following maps:

- Magnitude
- Retribution
- Intensity
- Delta Ruined
- CO2
- Hektik
- Nitra
- Gothra
- Abyss
- Underground
- Fallout
- Fissure Fall
- Chiron TL35
